							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/fictionnonfiction/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-23-at-1.03.15-PM-100x100.png" width="100" height="100" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Screen-Shot-2019-01-23-at-1.03.15-PM.png 2x" alt="Fiction Non Fiction" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/fictionnonfiction/">Fiction Non Fiction</a></h6>
										Hosted by Whitney Terrell and V.V. Ganeshananthan, <em>Fiction/Non/Fiction</em> interprets current events through the lens of literature, and features conversations with writers of all stripes, from novelists and poets to journalists and essayists.																			</div>
